Make Pair Key be List with "x" and "y"
Make Settings be Map with Pair Key meaning "grid" and "theme" meaning "calm"

Say Use Map Get with Settings and Pair Key and Otherwise be "missing"

Use Map Put with Settings and "level" and 271
Say Use Map Keys with Settings
Say Use Map Values with Settings

Make Public Settings be Use Map Merge with Settings and Map with "theme" meaning "bright"
Say Use Map Get with Public Settings and "theme" and Otherwise be "none"

Make Maybe Missing be Use Map Get with Settings and "missing" as Maybe String
Match Maybe Missing
  When Some Value
    Say Value
  When nothing
    Say "missing key"
